			<p>
				Bolivia was full of natural beauty. The thing about Bolivia is that it is completely authentic. Even the “touristy” areas of Bolivia were still less touristy than anywhere else we visited on our trip. For this reason it is amazing and difficult. Especially as a first place to start, it will be a culture shock. 
			</p>
